<view class="page breath-page theme-toolbox">
  <view class="page-head floral-title-box title-pattern-card"><image class="title-pattern-image" src="/assets/title-patterns/deep-purple.png" mode="aspectFill" /><view class="title-pattern-mask"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view><text class="eyebrow">安静小房间</text><text class="hero-title">深呼吸练习</text><text class="subtext">先不用立刻做决定。跟着呼吸，把自己从工作现场里拿回来一点。</text></view>
  <character-card image="{{companion.image}}" name="{{companion.name}}" tag="{{companion.tag}}" message="{{companion.message}}" sub-message="{{companion.subMessage}}" variant="{{companion.variant}}" size="{{companion.size}}" />
  <view class="amulet-card amulet-frame breath-card"><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--purple"></view><view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view><text class="amulet-frame__seal">呼吸护身符</text><view class="breath-ball {{phase.key}}"><text>{{phase.label}}</text></view><text class="phase-label">当前阶段：{{phase.label}}</text><text class="countdown">{{secondsLeft}}</text><text class="subtext">4 秒吸气 · 4 秒停留 · 6 秒呼气</text></view>
  <view class="control-row"><button class="sticker-button green {{running ? 'muted-button' : ''}}" bindtap="start">{{running ? '进行中' : '开始'}}</button><button class="sticker-button secondary {{running ? '' : 'muted-button'}}" bindtap="pause">暂停</button><button class="sticker-button" bindtap="reset">重置</button></view>
  <view class="note-card safety"><text>如果你正在经历严重身体不适、持续惊恐或无法保证安全，请优先联系现实中可信任的人或当地紧急帮助。</text></view>
</view>
